    <item>
      <title>标普将 CVC 支持的立顿茶评级进一步下调至垃圾级，因业绩和成本不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/s-p-cuts-cvc-backed-lipton-teas-deeper-into-junk-on-weak-results-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将立顿茶及冲剂母公司的评级进一步下调至垃圾级，指出这家茶叶制造商的业绩弱于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/s-p-cuts-cvc-backed-lipton-teas-deeper-into-junk-on-weak-results-costs</guid>
