      <title>早期冰层堆积导致北极东部无法通行俄罗斯液化天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/early-ice-build-up-closing-east-arctic-to-sanctioned-russian-lng</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯批准的北极液化天然气二号项目仅剩不到一个月的时间通过北海航线向亚洲运送液化气货物，之后该航道将关闭，直至明年夏天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/early-ice-build-up-closing-east-arctic-to-sanctioned-russian-lng</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
