    <item>
      <title>OPEC 下调对不受约束的石油需求增长的预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/opec-doubles-down-on-forecast-for-unfettered-oil-demand-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 再次预测全球石油需求将持续增长至本世纪中叶，科学家表示，这种异常观点将导致气候灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/opec-doubles-down-on-forecast-for-unfettered-oil-demand-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降息可能性上升，两年期美国国债收益率接近 2024 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-two-year-yields-fall-before-auction-as-rate-cut-odds-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者信心指数暴跌，短期美国国债收益率周二接近今年最低水平，这增加了美联储下个月再次降息半个百分点的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-two-year-yields-fall-before-auction-as-rate-cut-odds-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
